QuickeR Please accept accessing to your storage to use this application from settings Service name Take a screen shot of the QR Code you want to register,
and add it from the + button below. Add Other service Delete Cancel Are you sure you want to delete this service? Once it can not be restored after you have deleted. Get started by adding your first QR Code from right bottom button. No registered services Are you sure you want to open following URL? Open close copy Services Add Service Register Scanning result QR code Open Source License Tap here to set the QR Code.
Select the image containing your QR code saved in advance by taking a screen shot. Tap here to set the service icon. It will be showed in home. Input the service name here. At last, tap here to complete.
Well done!! Deleted the service The Image is unavailable. Register with QuickeR This service has already registered.>
